sentences: Víctor Manuel San José Sánchez (born July 7, 1947) is a Spanish singer-songwriter.
He has been married to the Spanish singer and actress Ana Belén since 1972.
Víctor Manuel edited some singles an EP and an album by the former Spanish discography Belter from 1966 to 1969

In 1978 Víctor Manuel signed for CBS.
However, five of Víctor's six albums resulted in commercial hits, with four number ones and 12 songs out of 60 at the Top 40 from 1979 to 1986.
